attributes.body:
Given Freedom;   
not from this system;  
embolden the swollen, vicious with pride.  

Kleptocracy;  
institutions’ occupation;  
plan for subjugation, for paper we die.  

*Cha-ching!*  

Raising the mountain, and bringing it down.  
Won’t stop destruction, til change comes around.  
A vicious construction, where blood turns to steel.  
Truth now subjective, only the question is real.  
Lust for the problem, hold it in your hand.  
Sweat for destruction, it’s supply and demand.  

But hey, there’s convenient stuff to buy,   
and for right now, you can still go outside.  
You’re always being watched, so no need to hide.  

*Cha-ching!*  

Consolidate;  
power and land;  
pay all the governments, then subjugate them.  

Neo-feudal;  
making oligarchs kings;  
buying allegiance while we’re gathering things.
